Description: The living atlas community provides tools to enable users
    of biodiversity information to find, access, combine and visualise data on
    plants, animals and fungi. 'galah' enables the R community to directly 
    access data and resources hosted by the living atlases.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
